@Jomi#13943 Tikz paket za LaTeX, ali treba se naviknuti na to

Možda i ima nešto lakše, ali nikad nećeš imati toliko mogućnosti. Primjer iz zadaće za jedan drugi predmet:

```
\begin{tikzpicture}[->,shorten >=1pt,auto,node distance=4cm,thick,font=\small,
    base/.style={circle,draw,minimum size=50pt,text width=1.6cm, text centered},
    entry/.style={double,circle,draw,minimum size=50pt,text width=1.6cm, text centered}]

    \node[entry] (1)
    {
        $req = \bot$
        $st = busy$
        $\overline{req} = \top$
    };
    \node[base, below of=1] (2)
    {
        $req = \top$
        $st = busy$
        $\overline{req} = \top$
    };
    \node[base, right of=2] (3)
    {
        $req = \top$
        $st = ready$
        $\overline{req} = \bot$
    };
    \node[base, above of=3] (4)
    {
        $req = \bot$
        $st = ready$
        $\overline{req} = \bot$
    };

    \path[]
        (1) edge node[below] {} (2)
        (2) edge node[right] {} (3)
        (3) edge node[above] {} (4)
        (4) edge node[left]  {} (1)
\end{tikzpicture}
```

